Class TileItemQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • rs.kreme.ksbot.api.queries.Query<KSGroundItem,​TileItemQuery>
      • rs.kreme.ksbot.api.queries.TileItemQuery
  • public class TileItemQuery
extends Query<KSGroundItem,​TileItemQuery>
    A specialized query class for filtering and retrieving ground items in the game. Extends the generic Query class and integrates contextual game utilities.
